{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1631253768.7095938", "card_id": "Q_485808612", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 283}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待越来越多高校教授「走红」网络，更受年轻人喜爱？你都遇到过哪些有趣的老师？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "随着视频资讯的普及，通过视频学习知识的年轻人越来越多。近几年，一些知识储备丰富的高校教师也纷纷在社交平台注册账号，在线「授课」，不少老师将年轻人关心的热门话题信手拈来，戴锦华、沈奕斐等教授更是受到了众多年轻人的追捧。这一现象的原因是什么？你有哪些有趣的老师推荐？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-5df0a18f8a9a9bf87d8fd867443851d0_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2072 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485808612"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIvafD5uvRqao2EAMaCDcwMjM5MTU2INfR54kGMCk41QlAAHIJNDg1ODA4NjEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1631253768.7103155", "card_id": "Q_21210517", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 189}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何在逆境翻盘，有什么逆境翻盘的好例子？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "怎样去证明热血漫真实存在？｜大学第一课"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-40f644f5b8918a648b86555a839018be_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1512 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21210517"}}, "attached_info": "ClIIvafD5uvRqao2EAMaBjY2NDk1MyC00/KNBTAXOJAJQAFyCDIxMjEwNTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1631253768.7109802", "card_id": "Q_485476077", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 363}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果给你足够的时间精力和研究经费，你最想解决世界上的哪一个科学难题，从而造福全人类？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "未来科学大奖联合知乎科学发起「科学向未来」活动：2021 未来科学大奖 邀请科学家们，以及所有热爱科学的年轻一代参与回答，创作优质回答将有机会亲临 11 月未来科学大奖周现场，与世界知名科学家们近距离接触，共同探索未知！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-fc08b6c3a993176532fa7ac58b00c6a6_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1250 万热度"}, "